  "title": "Check box are displaying incorrect(Algolia)",
  "body": "We are using instantsearch.js and our ApplicationID:AD6JRJWKK2.\r\n\r\n\r\nCurerntly we are facing  issue with Checkbox(UI).\r\n\r\nSome times it displaying correctly but in some times it displaying double checkbox instead of one.\r\n\r\nCode for your reference.\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n      container: '#aopPractice',\r\n      attributeName: 'PracticeAreaName',\r\n      operator: 'or',\r\n      limit: 10,\r\n      templates: {\r\n          item: aopfacetTemplateCheckbox,\r\n          header: '<h6 class=\"group-heading\"><div class=\"facet-title\">Areas of Practice</div class=\"facet-title\"></div>'\r\n      }\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n\r\nPlease find attachment.\r\n\r\nNote:\r\nSame problem in Sortby also.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nMohan\r\n\r\n![screenshot_13](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/24403373/20913419/c1fb2612-bb9d-11e6-857e-2962236b6a00.png)\r\n",
